@startuml
title GPS实时追踪（复杂度 O(n³)）

actor 操作员 as op
participant "前端 Map" as front
participant "Gateway\nWebSocket" as gw
participant "zrws-collect" as svc
database "Redis" as cache
database "MySQL" as db

== 实时位置上报 ==
op -> front: 启动追踪
front -> gw: STOMP CONNECT
gw -> gw: JWT 鉴权
front -> gw: SUBSCRIBE /topic/mission.1024.gps
svc -> cache: [Redis] PUBLISH gps:1024 {lat,lng,alt,speed,heading}
gw -> front: STOMP MESSAGE {droneId,lat,lng,alt,speed,heading}
front -> front: Three.js 轨迹更新
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_mission_gps (批量 100条/次)

== 异常流程 ==
alt 信号丢失
    svc -> cache: [Redis] SET gps:1024:last_seen
    svc -> gw: STOMP /topic/mission.1024.alerts
    gw -> front: 信号丢失告警
    front -> op: 弹窗提示
else 偏离航线
    svc -> svc: 实时计算偏离距离 > 50m
    svc -> gw: STOMP /queue/errors
    gw -> front: 偏离航线告警
    front -> op: 红色轨迹标注
end

@enduml
